// @test regression/INV059-legacy-color-coercions
// @description Legacy (v4/v5) sources keep the cross-type coercions v6 dropped (INV059): string colors and color/string comparisons were real in those versions, and 63 corpus records across 6 v4/v5 files rely on them (G004 leniency). This v5 fixture must stay clean while the same shapes error under v6.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects no-errors

//@version=5
indicator("INV059 legacy")
col = close > open ? color.green : color.red
isGreen = col == "green" ? 1 : 0
plot(isGreen)
